http://www.mviv.es/es/pdf/revista/julio2007/s&amp;v_08091011.pdf.  
<b>39
</b></p>
<p>  <i>Economic Survey of Spain 2005: Stabilising the housing market</i>, available at http://www.oecd.org/ 
dataoecd/53/3/34586052.pdf<i>.</i> 
