Prof. Dr. Ludwig Kr&#228;mer, Environmental Crime in Europe; Rules of Sanctions, Europa Law 
Publishing, Avosetta Series (5), August 2004, chap. 10. 
<b>43
</b></p>
<p> &#8220;Few city councils have been able to stand the pressure of promoters, who have purchased 
large tracts of agricultural land at very low prices for which they have later obtained millions in 
