</b></p>
<p>  See http://www.20minutos.es/noticia/169534/0/vivienda/jovenes/hipotecas/ and 
http://www.cje.org/C12/C8/OBJOVI%2014%20(primer%20trimestre%2020/ 
Document%20 Library/notaintroductoria.pdf. 
<b>67
</b></p>
<p>  It has been also stated that this situation hampers mobility for workers and their opportunities 
to find work in other parts of the country. See for instance: The European Industrial Relations 
Observatory -EIRO, available at http://www.eurofound.europa.eu/eiro/2006/02/feature/ 
es0602207f.html or Cristina Barcel&#243;, Housing Tenure and Labour Mobility: A Comparison 
across European Countries, <i>Documentos de Trabajo</i>, <i>N&#186; 0603</i>, <i>Banco de Espa&#241;a</i>, 2006, available 
at http://www.bde.es/informes/be/docs/dt0603e.pdf. 
